me is a very fun game that you can play and relax especially after a long day.", "short_description": "This is a Gorilla Tag Fangame that is meant to be fun, social, and entertaining. There are frequent updates that add lots to the game every time. There are many things to do such as Only Up (many levels), or just relax and sit by a campfire and talk with friends or other players, or be adventurous and explore the map."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1faEvJOSdYVeA9mVGJE3ZA_GM2daBpi6kMSUn4jG1EWo/edit?usp=sharing", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Emmett O'toole", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/chimphangoutvr/home", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}, {"id": "1573854509480616"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "7884064881617449"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "449275884123460"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "449275884123460"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1712350500, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "449275884123460"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8106964405994161", "version": "1.1.2"}, "id": "969173104886646", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": fa